Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.30,0:02:44.18,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,WE GO!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.73,0:02:57.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...head for the New World, the second half of the Grand Line.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.93,0:03:03.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, no one has ever fully explored it
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.32,0:03:06.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,except for Gold Roger, King of the Pirates.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.30,0:03:12.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The New World has ruined many pirates' dreams and ambitions.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.33,0:03:16.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, Monkey D. Luffy,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.29,0:03:20.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,a boy whose body turned to rubber after he ate the Gum-Gum Fruit,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.66,0:03:22.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and his friends venture into that sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.04,0:03:26.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna become the King of the Pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.77,0:03:33.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After surviving a fierce battle at the Fish-Man Island,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.65,0:03:36.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the Straw Hats finally entered the New World,--
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.41,0:03:39.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the harshest sea ruled by the Four Emperors.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.63,0:03:43.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After receiving an emergency signal, they landed on Punk Hazard Island.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.66,0:03:48.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was a strange island divided into two parts; the Burning Lands and the Ice Lands.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.29,0:03:51.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't let them escape!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.60,0:03:52.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Room!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.43,0:03:59.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is this?! It's like a thin film...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.17,0:04:06.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shambles!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.23,0:04:18.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,E-Everybody, calm down!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.46,0:04:20.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's do a roll call!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.72,0:04:22.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Chopper!\N--Here!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.40,0:04:24.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Franky!\N--Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.03,0:04:26.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sanji-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.68,0:04:28.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.40,0:04:30.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nami-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.08,0:04:33.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're Nami... aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.51,0:04:34.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh-huh!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.96,0:04:38.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is going on here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.80,0:04:43.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You stupid pirate, don't push your luck!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.51,0:04:49.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You ate the Op-Op Fruit and you're the Modification Man, I believe!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.56,0:04:55.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stay out of his sword's reach!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.79,0:05:02.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys are in my way! Get out of the circle!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.40,0:05:03.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The circle?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.51,0:05:06.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,While you're in the circle he created,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.79,0:05:09.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you're like a patient on an operating table!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.00,0:05:11.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is his operating room.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.84,0:05:15.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He has total control over it and can manipulate anything as he pleases!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.53,0:05:16.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's the Surgeon of Death!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.88,0:05:20.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't do it, Tashigi!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.49,0:05:22.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your Haki is not strong enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.43,0:05:43.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.38,0:05:53.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"A Collision! Law vs. Vice Admiral Smoker!"
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.18,0:05:58.33,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,THE LABORATORY - IN FRONT OF THE MAIN ENTRANCE
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.21,0:06:33.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,C-Captain-chan got cut in half!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.71,0:06:41.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Hey, you're alive, aren't you?!\N--Tashigi-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.40,0:06:53.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.94,0:06:58.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How dishonorable! I got sliced but I'm still breathing!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.05,0:07:04.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you just kill me, Trafalgar?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.23,0:07:12.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You talk like a master swordsman.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.77,0:07:17.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me tell you something, Navy soldier girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.04,0:07:23.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The weak can't even pick their way to die!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.64,0:07:27.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.79,0:07:30.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't reach me with that sword.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.70,0:07:41.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can chop you more if you liked it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.32,0:07:50.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn you! Stop insulting our Captain-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.67,0:07:52.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain-chan, don't worry!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.37,0:07:55.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll riddle that fool with bullets!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.97,0:08:02.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bullets?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.28,0:08:06.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How did the bullets get here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.65,0:08:08.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where did the bullets that we shot go?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.00,0:08:11.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those are the bullets you shot.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.44,0:08:13.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I switched them with the snow falling over you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.45,0:08:17.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is he invincible?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.73,0:08:21.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get down! He's gonna cut everything again!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.76,0:08:24.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No one can stop his sword attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.73,0:08:29.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That bastard! Captain-chan, run!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.78,0:08:34.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.47,0:08:55.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Smo-yan!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.07,0:09:01.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Surgeon of Death--Trafalgar Law!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.22,0:09:04.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're just a pirate!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.73,0:09:07.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop messing with the Navy!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.01,0:09:22.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I feel an unpleasant energy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.54,0:09:26.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have Sea Prism Stone on the tip of your jitte, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.51,0:09:39.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no! The recoil made the sword cut the artwork!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.22,0:09:41.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The ship's gonna fall onto us!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.96,0:09:45.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's run! He doesn't want us to be here anyway!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.52,0:09:57.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't care if you're a Warlord or not!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.13,0:10:01.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just get out of my way!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.33,0:10:05.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Vice Admiral Smoker!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.87,0:10:08.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain-chan, let's get away!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.21,0:10:10.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--But...\N--He's no match for us!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.88,0:10:13.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,White Blow!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.01,0:10:19.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Run! Get out of the circle!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.24,0:10:39.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Th-They were strong... Too strong...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.31,0:10:42.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Straw Hat Luffy and his crew...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.54,0:10:47.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn! They took Boss Brownbeard with them!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.40,0:10:51.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-We got to help the Boss!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.47,0:10:54.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're cold-blooded pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.35,0:10:56.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know what they're gonna do to him!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.59,0:10:58.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Boss Brownbeard!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.03,0:11:02.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We have to let the Master know!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.04,0:11:05.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Follow me, those of you who can stand up!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.53,0:11:13.11,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,THE ICE LANDS - LUFFY'S GROUP
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.31,0:11:18.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard a huge noise. Was it Sanji and the others?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.49,0:11:22.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Alliga-taur!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.60,0:11:25.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You really don't know what happened to my crew?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.22,0:11:28.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up! I won't tell you anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.91,0:11:33.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fine. Then run faster! To the building that Brook saw!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.87,0:11:36.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We gotta save Nami and the others!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.30,0:11:40.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How humiliating to lose to such a squirt!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.65,0:11:45.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You robbed my people so cruelly of all they had, you cheap muggers!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.58,0:11:48.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't try to give us a bad name!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.29,0:11:51.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys attacked us first!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.14,0:11:54.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're showing no sign of remorse, alligator guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.47,0:12:00.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Brook, I know you don't feel cold because you don't have flesh...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.34,0:12:02.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So why did you steal the coat?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.83,0:12:04.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because I felt like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.13,0:12:10.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so happy to see you all again so I wanted to share in your feeling cold!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.50,0:12:14.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I feel bad that Nami and the others were abducted in those clothes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.15,0:12:17.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hope they don't get frostbite and lose their limbs.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.70,0:12:21.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Geez, Robin! Don't share those gruesome concerns!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.77,0:12:34.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Master, what should we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.91,0:12:37.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Law and Smoker are in a big battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.07,0:12:43.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is he thinking?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.52,0:12:45.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought the plan was just to make them go away.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.17,0:12:51.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But those escaped pirates took the kids in the Biscuit Room with them
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.39,0:12:53.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and ran into Law and the others at the front.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.87,0:12:57.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So the Navy saw the children?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.05,0:12:57.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.27,0:13:01.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's what I feared the most.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.34,0:13:05.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now they know something is going on on this island!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.27,0:13:10.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if we kill Smoker,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.12,0:13:12.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the Navy will become aware that something is wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.85,0:13:14.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought so.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.29,0:13:18.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You just got back - what are you doing now, Monet?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.55,0:13:21.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was them.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.66,0:13:26.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We should have paid better attention.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.53,0:13:30.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah, I forgot to mention.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.48,0:13:32.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Vegapunk's dragon and
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.32,0:13:35.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Brownbeard's Centaur Patrol Unit have been defeated.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.49,0:13:37.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--What?!\N--Unbelievable!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.96,0:13:40.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Which means those pirates you kidnapped along with
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.74,0:13:42.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,their ship had other crew members
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.71,0:13:45.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and they were in the Burning Lands already.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.34,0:13:51.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They made it across the lake and they'll be here in a matter of minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.67,0:13:55.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They were so strong. Now look.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.64,0:13:59.44,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,THE STRAW HATS ARE BACK
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.11,0:13:59.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure it was them.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.77,0:14:03.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Straw Hats...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.07,0:14:05.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure you have heard about them.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.59,0:14:09.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're an unforgivable archenemy not just for the Navy
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.02,0:14:11.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but for the World Government too.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.25,0:14:13.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The World Government, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.08,0:14:17.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If they're so notorious, maybe it's good for us!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.28,0:14:23.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whether it's the Straw Hats or Smoker,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.98,0:14:28.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we can get rid of all those troublemakers who are learning what's
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.56,0:14:30.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,going on on this island at once!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.86,0:14:34.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But Master, even if they're a group of misfits,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.26,0:14:36.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,if we kill all the G-5 soldiers,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.83,0:14:39.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the Navy would be on the alert, wouldn't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.23,0:14:42.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, we can just suppress things that are going to
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.71,0:14:44.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,happen on the island from now on.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.92,0:14:53.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Call Joker.\N--Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.60,0:15:17.39,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,A MOUNTAIN BEHIND THE LABORATORY SANJI'S GROUP
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.05,0:15:24.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We made it out from the backdoor but what should we do now?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.03,0:15:27.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even with this strange transformation going on,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.62,0:15:29.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we have to keep running for now!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.57,0:15:34.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?! It's super confusing!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.55,0:15:38.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Bros!\N--W-We're gonna freeze to die!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.56,0:15:41.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Deadly cold? I don't give a damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.53,0:15:45.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The samurai and the brats? I don't give a damn anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.80,0:15:46.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.04,0:15:49.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't there a camera somewhere?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.76,0:15:52.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanna take a picture before we return to normal!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.43,0:15:54.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What're you gonna take a picture of?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.14,0:15:56.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And stop having nosebleeds in my body!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.12,0:16:01.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is more important, Nami! Don't button up my aloha shirt!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.93,0:16:03.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you all okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.88,0:16:06.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know it's cold but hang on a little bit longer!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.42,0:16:09.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Spiral Bro is being kind! It's too creepy!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.90,0:16:13.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened? Did you get your bodies switched?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.87,0:16:16.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like that's what happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.59,0:16:18.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hang on, kids!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.72,0:16:22.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm being treated very differently from before.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.21,0:16:33.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't know humans felt this cold!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.26,0:16:39.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bros, stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.02,0:16:44.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's cold...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.43,0:16:47.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is it... I-I can't even move...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.78,0:16:49.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Me too!\N--I'm freezing too!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.21,0:16:53.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn! We shouldn't have taken them with us when
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.20,0:16:54.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we didn't know where to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.19,0:16:58.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't feel cold at all with this body.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.38,0:17:17.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pieces of the ship are falling like leaves off a tree!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.25,0:17:18.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay, Smo-yan?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.88,0:17:22.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain-chan, how is your body? Did they stick together?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.57,0:17:26.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, your right hand is my left foot!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.19,0:17:30.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My hands! Whose feet are these?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.11,0:17:32.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit! We're in big trouble!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.27,0:17:35.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We lost our means of communication and the ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.14,0:17:38.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought the Warlords were on our side! That bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.40,0:17:43.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey hey, Captain-chan, don't try to move! Stay here!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.55,0:17:50.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tashigi, keep this in mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.35,0:17:56.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pirates will always be pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.10,0:18:03.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pirates will be pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.35,0:18:42.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.46,0:18:47.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No one, not even pirates or Government allies,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.42,0:18:50.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,is allowed to be here on this island, Law!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.01,0:18:55.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That means you people are not allowed, either!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.83,0:19:00.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Law, why are you here on Punk Hazard?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.43,0:19:06.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I never understood why you joined the Warlords in the first place!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.74,0:19:09.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you up to?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.41,0:19:44.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What we need to do now is to achieve higher status.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.27,0:19:48.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pirates all over the world have started to pay respect
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.08,0:19:50.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to the Straw Hats because of the incident at Enies Lobby.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.43,0:19:52.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.02,0:19:57.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll put all my pride on the line and kick their asses in the New World!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.84,0:20:01.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whether it's the Straw Hats...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.70,0:20:06.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...or the Warlord who serves for the World Government - Trafalgar Law,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.46,0:20:10.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,pirates will be pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.66,0:20:40.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've never trusted you Warlords.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.33,0:20:45.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe that's the right thing to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.28,0:21:11.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Law!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.71,0:21:15.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is this place to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.69,0:21:19.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who's behind this?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.76,0:21:24.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you up to on this island?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.37,0:21:34.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you answer first?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.32,0:21:42.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you all up to?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.05,0:22:08.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are things that you can't see unless you change your standing, Smoker!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.47,0:22:12.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Scalpel!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.31,0:22:33.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My heart!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.51,0:22:52.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have to tell you anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.72,0:23:25.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Smoker collapses after his heart is stolen.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.78,0:23:27.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With Law looking down coldly before them,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.80,0:23:32.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the rage of Tashigi and the G-5 reaches\N its peak and they attempt an attack...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.75,0:23:34.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When Luffy suddenly appears!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.70,0:23:38.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The meeting between the two, \Nwho share a deep bond from the great war,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.06,0:23:40.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,causes the situation to drastically change!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.73,0:23:42.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the next episode of One Piece!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.06,0:23:44.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Meeting Again After Two Years!\NLuffy and Law!"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.48,0:23:46.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna be King of the Pirates!!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.63,0:23:48.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
